what_worked: Applied date_cte_isolate, dimension_cte_isolate: Converted implicit cross joins to explicit JOINs, materialized pre-filtered dimension and fact tables into separate CTEs before joining, and restructured the LEFT JOIN to avoid redundant catalog_sales scans.
why_it_worked: Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows; Pre-filtering all dimension tables into CTEs avoids repeated full-table scans
